{"tid":2338628,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩男子破壞港鐵站各囚26個月　官稱暴力沒合理化餘地","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T08:21:00.000Z","uid":241764,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0931c728355395fba6eceb4057386b828e83dac","tid":2338628,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:36:20.000Z","msg":"節錄:<br />\n<br />\n兩名男子去年破壞將軍澳港鐵站內設施，打碎至少14塊月台幕門，導致港鐵須支付逾200萬元維修費。他們早前承認控罪，在區域法院各被判囚26個月。<br />\n<br />\n練錦鴻質疑，即使兩人將車站打碎，他們感不滿的政策不會一夜間消失，社會不會立即變得人人平等，法庭同意兩人並非為個人利益犯案，且沒有攻擊對象，但他們根本不清楚他們想要的是甚麼。他又說，法庭不排除他們是受旁觀者鼓勵和道德上的支持而犯案，兩人犯案的手法離開他們追求的民主和平公義，愈來愈遠，判刑不能讓人以為年輕有理想就可以為所欲為，強調暴力就是暴力，沒有任何美化和合理化的餘地。<br />\n<br />\n練錦鴻又指，法庭參考過兩人的精神科報告，認為兩人有情緒問題，但未至於構成合理減刑因素。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566948-20201224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566948-20201224.htm&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MeojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=741afb7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566948-20201224.htm&h=32ef1266\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566948-20201224.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e07453ae4f31a21ef9b23948a8afcf9831606f79","tid":2338628,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39685c95e865edfad190c6b0a24975b217c4af9d","tid":2338628,"uid":356542,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0208bdbbd5f64e1aac4858d9e3a9d733512b36f","tid":2338628,"uid":356542,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1f546a24ad20d82191f5e1f923c074da2a986da","tid":2338628,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"39685c95e865edfad190c6b0a24975b217c4af9d","tid":2